am pretty sure I followed the directions correctly and created the 
correct environmental variable paths.  However, when I try to run one 
of the matlab demos, matlab doesn't recognize any of the terms in the 
demo files.  Any suggestions?  The directions I followed are at 
http://thermo.ece.olin.edu/Cantera.shtml.
